flowchart TD
    Start([Cron Trigger]) --> Director[Director Agent Starts]
    Director --> ReadState[Read WORKLOG.md<br/>AGENDA.md State]
    ReadState --> Decision{Work<br/>Needed?}
    
    Decision -->|No| Sleep[Sleep Until<br/>Next Cron]
    Sleep --> Start
    
    Decision -->|Yes| SpawnAgent[Spawn Subagent<br/>with Task]
    SpawnAgent --> WriteFiles[Subagent Writes<br/>Deliverables to Files]
    WriteFiles --> UpdateLog[Subagent Updates<br/>WORKLOG.md Status]
    UpdateLog --> GitCommit[Git Commit<br/>Checkpoint]
    GitCommit --> Notify[Discord Notification<br/>Task Complete]
    Notify --> Sleep
    
